{
  "stem": "1502.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they tried to drag out these things with the Jews, and this way they still had a few hundred Jews in reserve.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they could claim in-- in the headquarters in Berlin that there's still Jews in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's what we figured out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We couldn't figure out any other reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The-- so my brother, and I'll come back, he couldn't-- couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he went to a doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the doctor told him that he needs, he has to have an occupation, or it's not gonna be good with him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He-- he decided to try to get a job in the Jewish old age home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he did get a job in the Jewish old age home, but it was, it-- the risk to us became very, very great because he was moving out from the hiding place every day to the Jewish old age home.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my supposition is that one day he was followed, and that's how they found our hiding place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because it happened a short while after he started to work in that old age home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Now, what I have to come back is that while we were hiding-- in the beginning, when we were hiding, my brother and myself, we were always very active in the religious Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in every town in Europe, there was a committee.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The committee consisted of a delegate from each Zionist party.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were many Jewish Zionist parties.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was the left and the right and the middle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Each one had a delegate in that committee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That committee was called the Palestinian Office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The reason it was called Palestinian Office because the only work that committee was doing is, as you know, the British had the mandate Palestine.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
